{
  "stem": "162.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was just a wonderful, wonderful experience.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't want to go to Israel because I just-- I had had so much hardship during the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And things weren't so terrific over there either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I-- it wasn't that I didn't want to go there, I just wanted to go to America.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, that was my thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I want to be-- I want to go to America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had, because my parents were not in a concentration camp, and they were only in the ghetto for a short time in the beginning-- like six, eight months-- we have to prove that-- that we were in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to prove that, you know, that we indeed had hardships through the Holocaust and everything else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to prove who we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one of the couples that were in-- in the ghetto with my parents gave an affidavits-- affidavit and-- and signed off that they knew my parents in the ghetto, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So finally, in 1949, we were given permission and papers to come here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were sent to Minneapolis.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the reason we were sent to Minneapolis-- because while we were trying to come over here, somebody told my father, he said, besides your being a musician-- just like the uncle told him-- he said, you've got to put down another profession.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my mother wrote down that she was a seamstress.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because my grandfather, her father, was a tailor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she studied designing, and she modeled hands, and she would help my father-- my grandfather sew once in a while.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now my father, when he studied music, worked in the coat factory of his brother's in Berlin, while he was studying music.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
